title: The Beatles - Later...A Compilation   FLAC
description:
A lossless compilation of later Beatles music.  I made this for myself from various sources but maybe other folks would be interested.  Of course there's stuff either included or excluded that will be divisive but again this was for me and my taste.  These can fit onto 2 discs at just about the maximum length (a little less than 80 minutes) provided you do not have gaps between tracks.  I hope you enjoy.
